name: Xavier: Renegade Angel
description: Xavier Renegade Angel is a memecoin inspired by the cult TV character known for his bizarre appearance and abstract, philosophical rants. The project aims to build a creative, community-driven space where surreal humor, digital art, and experimental ideas are celebrated. It serves as a platform for artists, meme creators, and fans of absurdist media to connect and collaborate, with future plans to fund unique art initiatives and web-based creative tools.
